ations\", \"from\": 8463, \"to\": 8493}, {\"ngram\": \"civic and environmental movements\", \"from\": 8495, \"to\": 8528}, {\"ngram\": \"territorial committees\", \"from\": 8530, \"to\": 8552}, {\"ngram\": \"student collectives\", \"from\": 8557, \"to\": 8576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The coalition said it is \\\"fighting for the right to housing and for militanttradeunions, movements that have stood alongside the Palestinian people, and theGlobal Sumud Flotilla,\\\" the seaborne campaign to break Israel's blockade ofGaza.\", \"from\": 8580, \"to\": 8816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8709, \"end\": 8727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palestinian people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 8791, \"end\": 8797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999672582, \"rank\": 3.266151367443474e-11, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The coalition\", \"from\": 8580, \"to\": 8593}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 8619, \"to\": 8628}, {\"ngram\": \"housing\", \"from\": 8632, \"to\": 8639}, {\"ngram\": \"militanttradeunions\", \"from\": 8648, \"to\": 8667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Protesters also decried Decree Law 1660, which empowers police to preemptively detain people for up to 12 hours if they believe they may act disruptively, as well as \\\"stateracismagainstmigrantsand racialized people, and transfeminist anger against social and institutional patriarchy.\\\"\", \"from\": 8818, \"to\": 9103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Protesters\", \"from\": 8818, \"to\": 8828}, {\"ngram\": \"Decree Law\", \"from\": 8842, \"to\": 8852}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 8874, \"to\": 8880}, {\"ngram\": \"preemptively detain people\", \"from\": 8884, \"to\": 8910}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 12 hours\", \"from\": 8915, \"to\": 8929}, {\"ngram\": \"stateracismagainstmigrantsand racialized people\", \"from\": 8985, \"to\": 9032}, {\"ngram\": \"transfeminist anger\", \"from\": 9038, \"to\": 9057}, {\"ngram\": \"social and institutional patriarchy\", \"from\": 9066, \"to\": 9101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the vanguard of the protest march were about 50 people carrying cardboard trees representing larches they said were cut down to construct the new bobsleigh track in Cortina d'Ampezzo.\", \"from\": 9105, \"to\": 9291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9273, \"end\": 9290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cortina d'Ampezzo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}, {\"begin\": 9273, \"end\": 9290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cortina d'Ampezzo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vanguard\", \"from\": 9108, \"to\": 9120}, {\"ngram\": \"the protest march\", \"from\": 9124, \"to\": 9141}, {\"ngram\": \"about 50 people\", \"from\": 9147, \"to\": 9162}, {\"ngram\": \"cardboard trees\", \"from\": 9172, \"to\": 9187}, {\"ngram\": \"larches\", \"from\": 9201, \"to\": 9208}, {\"ngram\": \"the new bobsleigh track\", \"from\": 9246, \"to\": 9269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They held a banner reading, \\\"Century-old trees, survivors of two wars, sacrificed for 90 seconds of competition on a bobsleigh track costing \\u20ac124 million.\\\"\", \"from\": 9292, \"to\": 9447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a banner reading\", \"from\": 9302, \"to\": 9318}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Century-old trees\", \"from\": 9320, \"to\": 9338}, {\"ngram\": \"survivors\", \"from\": 9340, \"to\": 9349}, {\"ngram\": \"two wars\", \"from\": 9353, \"to\": 9361}, {\"ngram\": \"90 seconds\", \"from\": 9378, \"to\": 9388}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 9392, \"to\": 9403}, {\"ngram\": \"a bobsleigh track\", \"from\": 9407, \"to\": 9424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stefano Nutini, a 71-year-old protester,toldReutersthat \\\"I am here because these Olympics are unsustainable-economically, socially, and environmentally.\\\"\", \"from\": 9449, \"to\": 9602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stefano Nutini\", \"from\": 9449, \"to\": 9463}, {\"ngram\": \"a 71-year-old protester\", \"from\": 9465, \"to\": 9488}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 9524, \"to\": 9538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Onehealthcareworker at the protesttoldEuronews: \\\"It's public money that has been spent on a display window.\", \"from\": 9604, \"to\": 9711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Onehealthcareworker\", \"from\": 9604, \"to\": 9623}, {\"ngram\": \"the protesttoldEuronews\", \"from\": 9627, \"to\": 9650}, {\"ngram\": \"public money\", \"from\": 9658, \"to\": 9670}, {\"ngram\": \"a display window\", \"from\": 9694, \"to\": 9710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may be interesting to have these showcase events, but at a time when there is not enough money for essential things, it makes no sense to spend it in this way.\\\"\", \"from\": 9712, \"to\": 9875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these showcase events\", \"from\": 9742, \"to\": 9763}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 9772, \"to\": 9778}, {\"ngram\": \"enough money\", \"from\": 9797, \"to\": 9809}, {\"ngram\": \"essential things\", \"from\": 9814, \"to\": 9830}, {\"ngram\": \"no sense\", \"from\": 9841, \"to\": 9849}, {\"ngram\": \"this way\", \"from\": 9865, \"to\": 9873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another demonstrator said that the Olympics \\\"have not brought any wealth to the city of Milan and L